<body>
    <h1>Task 15 - RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"f20357be5456" id=3D"Task15-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"dd5750573a72" id=3D"Task15-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"49585cd53154">The purpose of this document is to provide a d=
etailed <strong>requirement analysis for implementing HTTPS security on an =
Nginx web server</strong>. The document outlines functional and non-functio=
nal requirements, system behavior, constraints, and risk considerations.</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"46b42b518198">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ad86c3a2-e0aa-4ead-81b2-90a77f1718ed">
<li local-id=3D"d15365f8-7202-4157-a14f-a568bbcd078e">
<p local-id=3D"d8a0a257bcd1"><strong>CTO</strong> =E2=80=93 to understand s=
ystem capabilities and security implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbe35562-aa1f-4e09-af6f-135ef3f9f56d">
<p local-id=3D"3e1e68eb75ea"><strong>Solution Architects</strong> =E2=80=93=
 to review system design and architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff05e9c4-b199-44dd-b03d-baba45a2f70f">
<p local-id=3D"64ecacd29451"><strong>DevOps Engineers</strong> =E2=80=93 to=
 implement and maintain server configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"875c8043-0917-4a5f-b259-ffcccb5a2658">
<p local-id=3D"bef1afcae981"><strong>Developers</strong> =E2=80=93 to under=
stand secure communication requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78dfc24b-88dd-42dc-b4c4-57d96d139e73">
<p local-id=3D"d45535e28f90"><strong>Resellers / Partners</strong> =E2=80=
=93 to understand deployment architecture</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2d0cbe18-ea84-446c-b974-8dd2583e5c68">
<h2 local-id=3D"e63fb30a971d" id=3D"Task15-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f7f1dd9ff5de">This project focuses on <strong>securing an Ng=
inx web server using SSL/TLS encryption and HTTP to HTTPS redirection</stro=
ng>.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ee375ddf126" id=3D"Task15-RAD-IncludedinScope">Included in=
 Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"64aaa5e1-ecfb-4c34-af92-57ecaa21a1e0">
<li local-id=3D"c42c46b6-d81c-41e1-a1a6-7e0a274ccc23">
<p local-id=3D"e4eba564436c">Installing and configuring <strong>Nginx web s=
erver</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c50f3fb-7632-438b-a1c0-3d8a2b6946e6">
<p local-id=3D"fe93c8b835d4">Generating <strong>self-signed SSL certificate=
</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9cb31a89-8af4-408b-b43e-b33aca3a11af">
<p local-id=3D"09e114932f51">Configuring <strong>HTTPS communication</stron=
g></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"07c56b11-115d-4316-831d-8a00f58cd40a">
<p local-id=3D"d233a12e7cfb">Implementing <strong>HTTP =E2=86=92 HTTPS redi=
rection</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5b07d66c-140b-4ce0-92ca-a03d6c2690a5">
<p local-id=3D"2db98f0e0546">Configuring <strong>basic security headers</st=
rong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ae04737-3cef-4fc9-8bce-672426f2f957">
<p local-id=3D"c9c4bdee8b35">Testing secure communication using <strong>bro=
wser and CLI tools</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"b51196d532da" id=3D"Task15-RAD-NotIncluded">Not Included</h=
3>
<ul local-id=3D"6f91cd95-81f8-4ce7-92dd-1fc8998910fa">
<li local-id=3D"c6a3dcdd-d3cb-4e85-a639-03017ae7cc29">
<p local-id=3D"869e7d109f18">Domain-based SSL certificates (e.g., Let's Enc=
rypt)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e19fe66-2bd0-451a-8998-d50c2ad276fd">
<p local-id=3D"decdd4d04c47">Load balancing or high availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"52937d0a-dfb0-4a0b-85da-41bc20ceaa63">
<p local-id=3D"6afda312e560">Advanced web application firewall configuratio=
ns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"06689399-6f17-49af-b110-7dd53fa3010b">
<p local-id=3D"52125186d36f">CI/CD automation pipelines</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b9ceb800-0195-4b61-baf6-686a1d40d7e3">
