<hr local-id=3D"17ec2057-2f20-4579-8250-ed99fd540a7c">
<h2 local-id=3D"b9b8ea04fe5f" id=3D"Task15-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<p local-id=3D"da8274bc17c5">The following references were used to create t=
his document:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"59617c18-1c41-4d55-b66c-50fabeaf8a15">
